------------------ Heya guys! - After about a week of on and off progress, here comes an updated version of my first ever released map. - JB_MC is a Jailbreak map with the 8bit feel of Minecraft. The map includes 4 cells, each with 3 spawns, a wall, 5 secrets, pool, cafeteria, kitchen, gun toss, shot 4 shot, spray wall, and a knife pit. - Some elements that make this map unique are the Minecraft textures, the hidden secrets, the food that can be used for health, and various randomized systems. For example, each cell has a 50% chance of allowing the prisoner to go to the Rebel Way. - This map is only in an early beta. I have worked out most of the problems. In the next versions expect any fixes that are addressed, more spawns, and a 3D skybox. - The map may be pretty big because I used PakRat to include all of the sounds and textures. ------------------ **FIXES** - Lighting! - 2 New Secrets (5 in total!) - Indoor Lighting (Breakable Glowstone!) - Bed Textures (Now aligned correctly!) - Cubemaps (Reflections!) - Cell 4 Leak - Changed Layout of CT Spawn/Stairs (allows for lighting to be added.) Thanks for all the help and support through out the development process of this map. If you see ANY problems at all, don't be afraid to post a comment, PM, or EMail (my EMail is on my profile.). Again, thanks! ------------------ ------------------

I have had this jailbreak map for about 2 years now, I just haven't ever been able to release it.  Finally I am, and I m proud with how it came out.  It's supposed to look like you are on the edge of a cliff, facing an ocean.  Careful though, because the fall will kill you if you decide you can't handle the pressure of being locked up every day in a small cell.

This map includes:

- Armory (With a prisoner warning system; The doors will lock shut for a little bit, and alert all the guards)
- Standard cell block
- Infirmary (Next to armory)
- 4 Corners Game
- Maze Game
- Shot 4 Shot
- Gun Toss
- Pool
- Disco
- Race
- Bunnyhop
- Soccer field
- Basketball court

Explore the layout as a guard, because you can go on top of the cellblock roof (there are ladders, and crouch jump areas).  There is also a guard tower near the pool for snipers.  So have fun with this map, because there is a lot of exploring to do, even if it looks like a small map.

Also, for the security system in armory, you need to press the button downstairs in armory to activate it.  Once activated, any prisoner who walks into the red beam will activate the security system.  The doors will close for a small amount of time, and the guards will be alerted.  Prisoners in the locked armory have a small opportunity to arm themselves before the guards get their.

Hello all,

This is my first map made in Source SDK. I think it was extremely difficult for a first timer to construct, but i think i did pretty well for my first map.

So here I present Jailbreak Asylum V2 (I hope the name isn't taken...)

Make sure to read the ReadMe file for proper setup.

[b]MAP FEATURES[/b]
===================================================================================
- Standard cell doors made from props that open at the push of a button. There are 16 cells. (and 16 CT spawn points) for a maximum of 32 players.
- Central arena -- This area is marked on the mini-map. It can be used for nearly anything. Be it guntoss, highest spreay, shot for shot you name it. Everything happens in the arena.
- Solitary confinement -- Solitary confinement is in the center of the arena with the 2 large metal doors. The buttons for the doors are located on either side of the cell door button marked "A" and "B".
- One way glass -- Most of the CT paths go behind T territory and the CT's are able to view a T up close without a T knowing due to one way glass. Look at last screenshot to see what i mean.
- Weapon recovery annex -- Make a weapon fall into the crack on the red side of the map and proceed to the lower level where the CT's spawn to retrieve it.
- Empty weapon pit -- Nothing much, just a hole to throw empty guns into, because i hate accidentally picking up an empty weapon.
- A few secrets and easter eggs -- You'll have to find them yourself ;)
- There is no V1 so don't look for it. (I called it V2 cause i had a map similar to this but it became FUBAR)

[b]OTHER NOTES[/b]
===================================================================================
- Feel free to optimise the map for Garry's Mod. Just make sure to give me credit.
- I'm open for compilations with other's if your interested. My steam name is INSTAGIBmaniac. If you have any questions comments, email me at chew-mann@hotmail.com. Please try to be positive!

Hi everyone,

Today, i'm happy to show you my new map jb_iceworld
I made this map in one month and i hope you'll like it.
I have to say that this map is a Jailbreak map for Counter Strike-Source, so i've focused the most in mini-games (less in the "beautifull aspect"), and the main part of buttons/commands are filtered for CTs, and only Ts can play the games.
For exemple, if you want to try the "Hunger game", you need at least to be 2. For a question of optimization, models in cells are delete when jails open, if you want to see them, play terrorist.



jb_iceworld
==================
For Christmas, the Director Raphi decided that even his prisonners can enjoy this party. He transfered them in a new prison named "Iceworld" which is full of magical and funny element.
Don't worry, in this prison, terrorist won't be tired, this new place came with a lot of new games and activities


Games
==================
14 games. I guess it's good for a jb map :)

- Couch Room : 2 couches will be killed

- Death Crate : Terrorists will have do dodge a death crate

- Jump Rope : As his name, Ts have to jump to dodge the sugar cane

- Pacman : Ts have to go into the house and are resized. Cts have to follow and cut them

- Climb : As every climb, Ts just have to climb to the end.

- Avalanche : Ts have to up the hill in dodging the snow

- Race : It's a funny race, with half-pipe/surf/dodge.

- Hunger game : When a CT will unable the game, Ts will be teleported on the big ice block and will have to knife to the death.

- Hockey : It's the football... but it's Hockey 

- Disco : I've put 3 new songs for your ears (let it goooo let it gooo)

- Carebear say : The carebear will give you order and you'll have to try to dodge his attacks. If you fail, you die, it's simple. (This game need some experience)

- Longjump : You have to do the surf and then Jump the farthest. When CTs will press the button, the 3 farthest will win.

- The Snake : It's a simple Gravity-Race


Secrets & Event
==================
In this map, i've put some secret and a special event.
I guess you'll discover yourself vents, but i'll explain how to enable the event, it's not automatic.

You have to put the noclip and go under the main room, you'll found 2 buttons and a knife. Press a button, it will only enable a song (The left one, a french song, the right one, an english song).
With the knife, you'll be able to spawn present on the floor, just press "e" to spawn them. When Ts will cut them, they'll win 4 points in their score.


Thank you for watching, Have fun :)
